Install Instructions
====================
Generally, use following commands to compile and install brasd:

./configure --prefix=/usr
make
sudo make install
sudo make install-service

Andvanced Options
=================
use "./configure --disable-client" to diable the compiling of bras-client.

"make install-service" will install bras as a system daemon on your
computer. To uninstall the daemon, use "make uninstall-service".
